                    <img src="~/css/monoboard.jpg" alt="Mortgage Step 1" class="w-4/5 mx-auto mb-4" />
                    <h5 class="text-lg mb-1">Step 2: Click the "Mortgage" button on the land you want to mortgage.</h5>
                    <img src="~/css/managesytem.jpg" alt="Mortgage Step 2" class="w-4/5 mx-auto mb-4" />
                    <h5 class="text-lg mb-1">Step 3: Your plot of land has been mortgaged. The corresponding mortgage amount will be added to your balance.</h5>
                    <img src="~/css/mortgage.jpg" alt="Mortgage Step 3" class="w-4/5 mx-auto mb-4" />
                    <img src="~/css/monoboard_mortgage.jpg" alt="Mortgage Step 3" class="w-4/5 mx-auto mb-4" />
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mt-4">Un-mortgage</h4>
                    <h5 class="text-lg mb-1">Step 1: Click on the “Manage” button.</h5>
                    <img src="~/css/monoboard.jpg" alt="Un-mortgage Step 1" class="w-4/5 mx-auto mb-4" />
