                    <img src="~/css/tradingsystem.jpg" alt="Offer Price Step 2" class="w-4/5 mx-auto mb-4" />
                    <h5 class="text-lg mb-1">Step 3: Click to select the asset you want to offer.</h5>
                    <img src="~/css/tradingsystem_asset.jpg" alt="Offer Price Step 3" class="w-4/5 mx-auto mb-4" />
                    <h5 class="text-lg mb-1">Step 4: You can use the slider to offer the price you want, or you can both choose your property and offer money in exchange.</h5>
