                    <h4 class="text-lg mb-1">Step 2: Dialog will confirm whether you are sure or not. If you choose "Yes", you have confirmed that you are bankrupt and will be removed from the game. If "No" is selected, the system will cancel the action.</h4>
                    <img src="~/css/bankrupt.jpg" alt="Bankrupt Step 2" class="w-4/5 mx-auto mb-4" />
                    <h4 class="text-lg mb-1">Step 3: The "Game Over" screen will appear on your screen as soon as you lose. You can choose "Restart" or "Exit to Menu".</h4>
                    <img src="~/css/gameover.jpg" alt="Bankrupt Step 3" class="w-4/5 mx-auto mb-4" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

